{
  "name": "Expert Druid",
  "type": "feature",
  "img": "icons/magic/nature/tree-animated-squint.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You gain the following benefits for your Druid Class Features.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Druid Domain</span></strong></span></p><p>The number of Domain Spaces you create increases to 10.</p><p><strong>Losing Domain Spaces:</strong> A Domain Space disappears if you end your turn farther than 20 Spaces away from it.</p><p>You can spend additional MP when you use Druid Domain to increase the number of Domain Spaces created by 8 per additional MP spent.</p><p><strong>Wild Growth:</strong> You can spend additional MP to increase the healing by 1 per 2 additional MP spent.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Wild Form</span></strong></span></p><p>Your Wild Forms have +1 HP and 1 additional Trait Point.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Nature’s Torrent</span></strong></span></p><p>The range of Nature’s Torrent increases to 15 Spaces.</p><p>When you use Nature’s Torrent, you can spend MP to enhance its effects:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Vulnerability: (2 MP) </strong>The Vulnerability increases by 1.</p></li><li><p><strong>Area: (X MP) </strong>The diameter of the Sphere increases by X.</p></li></ul>",
